{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id4660248a-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6031"},"text":"§ 6031.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Return of partnership income","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4660248b-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" General rule","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Every partnership (as defined in section 761(a)) shall make a return for each taxable year, stating specifically the items of its gross income and the deductions allowable by subtitle A, and such other information, for the purpose of carrying out the provisions of subtitle A as the Secretary may by forms and regulations prescribe, and shall include in the return the names and addresses of the individuals who would be entitled to share in the taxable income if distributed and the amount of the distributive share of each individual.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4660248c-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Copies to partners","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Each partnership required to file a return under subsection (a) for any partnership taxable year shall (on or before the day on which the return for such taxable year was required to be filed) furnish to each person who is a partner or who holds an interest in such partnership as a nominee for another person at any time during such taxable year a copy of such information required to be shown on such return as may be required by regulations. Information required to be furnished by the partnership under this subsection may not be amended after the due date of the return under subsection (a) to which such information relates, except—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4660248d-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" in the case of a partnership which has elected the application of section 6221(b) for the taxable year,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4660248e-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" as provided in the procedures under section 6225(c),","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4660248f-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" with respect to statements under section 6226, or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id46602490-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" as otherwise provided by the Secretary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id46602491-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Nominee reporting","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Any person who holds an interest in a partnership as a nominee for another person—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id46602492-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" shall furnish to the partnership, in the manner prescribed by the Secretary, the name and address of such other person, and any other information for such taxable year as the Secretary may by form and regulation prescribe, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id46602493-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" shall furnish in the manner prescribed by the Secretary such other person the information provided by such partnership under subsection (b).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id46602494-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Separate statement of items of unrelated business taxable income","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of any partnership regularly carrying on a trade or business (within the meaning of section 512(c)(1)), the information required under subsection (b) to be furnished to its partners shall include such information as is necessary to enable each partner to compute its distributive share of partnership income or loss from such trade or business in accordance with section 512(a)(1), but without regard to the modifications described in paragraphs (8) through (15) of section 512(b).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id46602495-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Foreign partnerships","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id46602496-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/e/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Exception for foreign partnership","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Except as provided in paragraph (2), the preceding provisions of this section shall not apply to a foreign partnership.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id46602497-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/e/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Certain foreign partnerships required to file return","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Except as provided in regulations prescribed by the Secretary, this section shall apply to a foreign partnership for any taxable year if for such year, such partnership has—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id46602498-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/e/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" gross income derived from sources within the United States, or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id46602499-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/e/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" gross income which is effectively connected with the conduct of a trade or business within the United States.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary may provide simplified filing procedures for foreign partnerships to which this section applies.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4660249a-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6031/f"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"f"},"text":"(f)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Electing investment partnerships","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of any electing investment partnership (as defined in section 743(e)(6)),","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002280"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002280"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" the information required under subsection (b) to be furnished to any partner to whom section 743(e)(2) applies shall include such information as is necessary to enable the partner to compute the amount of losses disallowed under section 743(e)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id4660249b-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1954-08-16/ch736"},"text":"Aug. 16, 1954, ch. 736","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/68A/741"},"text":"68A Stat. 741","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/tXIX/s1906/b/13/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, title XIX, § 1906(b)(13)(A)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-04"},"text":"Oct. 4, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/1834"},"text":"90 Stat. 1834","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/248/tIV/s403"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–248, title IV, § 403","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-09-03"},"text":"Sept. 3, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/669"},"text":"96 Stat. 669","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/514/tXV/s1501/c/16"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–514, title XV, § 1501(c)(16)","children":[],"tail":", title XVIII, § 1811(b)(1)(A), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-10-22"},"text":"Oct. 22, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/2740"},"text":"100 Stat. 2740","children":[],"tail":", 2832; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/647/tV/s5074/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–647, title V, § 5074(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-11-10"},"text":"Nov. 10, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/3682"},"text":"102 Stat. 3682","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/34/tXI/s1141/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–34, title XI, § 1141(a)","children":[],"tail":", title XII, § 1223(a), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-08-05"},"text":"Aug. 5, 1997","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/111/980"},"text":"111 Stat. 980","children":[],"tail":", 1019; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/357/tVIII/s833/b/4/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–357, title VIII, § 833(b)(4)(B)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2004-10-22"},"text":"Oct. 22, 2004","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/118/1590"},"text":"118 Stat. 1590","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/74/tXI/s1101/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–74, title XI, § 1101(e)","children":[],"tail":", (f)(1), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-11-02"},"text":"Nov. 2, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/637"},"text":"129 Stat. 637","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/113/dQ/tIV/s411/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–113, div. Q, title IV, § 411(d)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/3122"},"text":"129 Stat. 3122","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/141/dU/tII/s206/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–141, div. U, title II, § 206(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-03-23"},"text":"Mar. 23, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/1178"},"text":"132 Stat. 1178","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id4660249c-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id4660249d-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id4660249e-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 743(e)(6), referred to in subsec. (f), was redesignated section 743(e)(5) by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/97/tI/s13504/b/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–97, title I, § 13504(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2017-12-22"},"text":"Dec. 22, 2017","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/131/2142"},"text":"131 Stat. 2142","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id4660249f-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2018—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/141"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–141","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Information required to be furnished by the partnership under this subsection may not be amended after the due date of the return under subsection (a) to which such information relates, except—” for “Except as provided in the procedures under section 6225(c), with respect to statements under section 6226, or as otherwise provided by the Secretary, information required to be furnished by the partnership under this subsection may not be amended after the due date of the return under subsection (a) to which such information relates.” and added pars. (1) to (4)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2015—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/113"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–113","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Except as provided in the procedures under section 6225(c), with respect to statements under section 6226, or as otherwise provided by the Secretary, information required to be furnished by the partnership under this subsection may not be amended after the due date of the return under subsection (a) to which such information relates.” for “In the case of an electing large partnership (as defined in section 775), such information shall be furnished on or before the first March 15 following the close of such taxable year.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/74/s1101/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–74, § 1101(e)","children":[],"tail":", (f)(1), which directed amendment of subsec. (b) by first inserting at end “Except as provided in the procedures under section 6225(c), with respect to statements under section 6226, or as otherwise provided by the Secretary, information required to be furnished by the partnership under this subsection may not be amended after the due date of the return under subsection (a) to which such information relates.” and then by striking the last sentence, was not executed in view of the amendment by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/113"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–113","children":[],"tail":", which made identical amendments but in the reverse order, effective as if included in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/74/s1101"},"text":"section 1101 of Pub. L. 114–74","children":[],"tail":". See note above."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2004—Subsec. (f). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/357"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–357","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (f)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1997—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/34/s1223/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–34, § 1223(a)","children":[],"tail":", inserted at end “In the case of an electing large partnership (as defined in section 775), such information shall be furnished on or before the first March 15 following the close of such taxable year.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/34/s1141/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–34, § 1141(a)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (e)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1988—Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/647"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–647","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (d)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1986—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/514/s1501/c/16"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–514, § 1501(c)(16)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “was required to be filed” for “was filed” and “required to be shown on such return” for “shown on such return”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/514/s1811/b/1/A/i"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–514, § 1811(b)(1)(A)(i)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “or who holds an interest in such partnership as a nominee for another person” after “who is a partner”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/514/s1811/b/1/A/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–514, § 1811(b)(1)(A)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (c)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1982—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/248/s403/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–248, § 403(b)","children":[],"tail":", designated existing provisions as subsec. (a) and added subsec. heading."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/248/s403/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–248, § 403(a)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (b)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1976—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455","children":[],"tail":" struck out “or his delegate” after “Secretary”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id466024a0-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id466024a1-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2018 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/141/dU/tII/s207"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–141, div. U, title II, § 207","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-03-23"},"text":"Mar. 23, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/1183"},"text":"132 Stat. 1183","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/115/141/dU/tII/s207"},"text":"“The amendments made by this title [amending this section and sections 6201, 6211, 6221, 6222, 6225 to 6227, 6231 to 6235, 6241, 6501, 6651, 6696, 6698, 6702, 6724, and 7485 of this title] shall take effect as if included in section 1101 of the Bipartisan Budget Act of 2015 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/74"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–74","children":[],"tail":"].”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id466024a2-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2015 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/113/dQ/tIV/s411/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–113, div. Q, title IV, § 411(e)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/3122"},"text":"129 Stat. 3122","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/114/113/dQ/tIV/s411/e"},"text":"“The amendments made by this section [amending this section and sections 6225, 6226, 6234, and 6235 of this title] shall take effect as if included in section 1101 of the Bipartisan Budget Act of 2015 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/74"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–74","children":[],"tail":"].”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/74"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–74","children":[],"tail":" applicable to returns filed for partnership taxable years beginning